North Terrace in the heart of Adelaide.
 
Keynote Speaker: Paul Carter, author of The Road to Botany Bay and Living
in a New Country.
 
Dorothy Green Memorial Lecture: Drusilla Modjeska, author of Exiles at Home
and Poppy.
 
