abt his statement is the underlying apprehension of _interdisciplinarity_
in art, scholarship and reseach, the whole thing. and in the final
analysis, what charles' comment reminds me of is the crucial relation
between interdisciplinarity and the real cutting edge of art.  --and that's
a great place to be if you really want to be there
 
