Subject:      EPC Magazine entries -- status report --
 
Here is a list of magazines currently having entries in the EPC. (With
the exception of Juxta, just received.) Obviously, there are many more
relevant entries. Hopefully, we can develop these entries, but this is
where we are this moment:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
                           ELECTRONIC POETRY CENTER
 
   Chain / Buffalo (Cite)
   Coppertales / Australian Writing Online / Sidney, Australia (Cite)
   El-e-phant: A Language Arts Review / Los Angeles (Cite)
   First Intensity / Staten Island (Cite)
   Impercipient / Providence (Cite)
   Interruptions / Kent OH (Cite)
   Kiosk / Buffalo (Cite)
   Little Magazine / Albany (Cite)
