I don't know where writing comes from, only where it sometimes comes
from for me. It comes in the fog of the thoudsand-and-one things like
a sharp prick in the bum/ribs/eye andf the little shout/gasp/curse I
exhale is a poem/story/poemstory and then I have this piece of
writing and the thousand-and-one things--again.
