not read much, I remember that when I was a graduate student and a
bunch of topics were suggested, I would always take the one I knew
least about. It made for learning instead of whatever we do with our
favourite things. Simil;ar process when teaching a book: you have to
learn something, and who wants to keep on teaching what he knows?
