Brathwaites _Middle Passage_ was made available years ago on a series of
LP's.  I've got about two thirds of the set.  I also have tape of
Brathwaite reading at UC Santa Cruz a few years ago.  Tapes may be in San
Jose, Michael, which means I may not be able to retrieve them till late
August, but I'll let you know.  Maybe I've got at least one here in L.A.
-- Meanwhile, I wanted everybody to know about that older set -- might
check local media collections to see if they have any of it.  Brathwaite
reads beautifully, thoug, as veterans of his readings know, the program
may go on for hours!
 
a.l.nielsen
